{"metadata":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","modules":[{"name":"GLibObject"}],"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GLibObject","externalID":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolPAAE12addToggleRef6notify4datayySvSg_SpySo8_GObjectVGSgs5Int32VtXCSg_AGtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:10GLibObject0B0C"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glibobject\/object\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"notify"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify","text":"GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This functionality is intended for binding "},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to a proxy","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object managed by another memory manager. This is done with two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"paired references: the strong reference added by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"text":" and a reverse reference to the proxy","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"object which is either a strong reference or weak reference.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The setup is that when there are no other references to ","type":"text"},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"only a weak reference is held in the reverse direction from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to the proxy object, but when there are other references held to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"object"},{"text":", a strong reference is held. The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"text":" callback is called","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when the reference from ","type":"text"},{"code":"object","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to the proxy object should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“toggled” from strong to weak ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"is_last_ref"},{"type":"text","text":" true) or weak to strong"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"is_last_ref"},{"text":" false).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Since a (normal) reference must be held to the object before","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"type":"text","text":", the initial state of the reverse"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"link is always strong."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Multiple toggle references may be added to the same gobject,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"however if there are multiple toggle references to an object, none","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of them will ever be notified until all but one are removed.  For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this reason, you should only ever use a toggle reference if there"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is important state in the proxy object.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Note that if you unref the object on another thread, then ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"notify"},{"type":"text","text":" might"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"still be invoked after "},{"code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", and the object argument","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"might be a dangling pointer. If the object is destroyed on other threads,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you must take care of that yourself."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_object_add_toggle_ref()"},{"text":" must be released with ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_object_remove_toggle_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object/addToggleRef(notify:data:)":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Increases the reference count of the object by one and sets a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"callback to be called when all other references to the object are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dropped, or when this is already the last reference to the object"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and another reference is established."}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addToggleRef"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"notify","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GToggleNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gobject.h@T@GToggleNotify"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?)","kind":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object\/addtoggleref(notify:data:)","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/addToggleRef(notify:data:)","title":"addToggleRef(notify:data:)","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Object","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"Object","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The base object type.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Object"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject/Object/ObjectProtocol-Implementations":{"kind":"article","title":"ObjectProtocol Implementations","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject\/Object\/ObjectProtocol-Implementations","abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/glibobject\/object\/objectprotocol-implementations","role":"collectionGroup"},"doc://GLibObject/documentation/GLibObject":{"abstract":[],"title":"GLibObject","url":"\/documentation\/glibobject","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLibObject\/documentation\/GLibObject"}}}